## SCOPE & BOUNDARIES

**In scope**
- `{{COMPANY}}`'s corporate structure: parent entity, all divisions / business units / operating groups / regional offices / named subsidiaries (verify `{{KNOWN_DIVISIONS}}` if provided; discover the rest).
- Every project where `{{COMPANY}}` is GC / CM / builder — active and completed within `{{LOOKBACK_YEARS}}` years, up to `{{MAX_PROJECTS}}`. Map each to its division. Weight `{{SECTOR_FOCUS}}` sectors first when prioritizing depth.
- Firmographics: HQ, founding year, revenue, employees, ENR rank, ownership.
- Office/location footprint (all physical offices, especially in `{{REGION_HINT}}`).
- Industry events (sponsor/exhibitor/attendee) and trade-association memberships.
- Incumbent construction software / tech stack (PM, BIM, estimating, field, risk).
- Hard risk & compliance data: EMR/TRIR/DART/OSHA, bonding & surety, insurance, litigation, liens, licenses, certifications (ISO/MBE/WBE/DBE/8(a)).
- Per-project hard attributes: full address + parcel, delivery method, contract type, procurement route, full date set (announce → award → permit → groundbreak → NTP → top-out → completion), size metrics, permit numbers & valuations, funding source, hazard zones.
